-For what?

603
00:46:57,648 --> 00:46:58,938
For taking it.

604
00:47:03,854 --> 00:47:04,904
The rat!

605
00:47:07,258 --> 00:47:09,917
-But he is a...
-I just dropped my keys.

606
00:47:13,964 --> 00:47:15,604
Have you decided this evening?

607
00:47:15,933 --> 00:47:19,503
-Your soup is excellent. But...
-But we order it every time.

608
00:47:20,104 --> 00:47:23,234
-What else do you have?
-Well, we have a very nice foie gras.

609
00:47:23,774 --> 00:47:24,703
