623
00:47:58,576 --> 00:48:00,746
A lot of customers like the soup.
That's all we are saying.

624
00:48:01,145 --> 00:48:02,515
Were we saying that?

625
00:48:03,547 --> 00:48:06,127
Very well. If it's Linguini they want,

626
00:48:06,584 --> 00:48:10,594
tell them Chef Linguini has prepared
something special for them.

627
00:48:11,255 --> 00:48:13,975
Something definitely off menu.

628
00:48:14,759 --> 00:48:16,159
Oh, and don't forget to stress

629
00:48:16,460 --> 00:48:18,630
