634
00:48:33,778 --> 00:48:35,917
Are you sure?
That recipe was a disaster.

635
00:48:36,313 --> 00:48:37,833
Gusteau himself said so.

636
00:48:38,149 --> 00:48:41,109
Just the sort of challenge
a budding chef needs.

637
00:48:41,852 --> 00:48:43,022
"Sweetbread a la Gusteau.

638
00:48:43,287 --> 00:48:45,477
"Sweetbread cooked
