00:49:42,746 --> 00:49:44,206
I'm going to pick that up.

656
00:49:44,515 --> 00:49:46,444
I got some of that spice.

657
00:49:47,618 --> 00:49:48,668
Okay.

658
00:49:49,053 --> 00:49:50,042
What are you doing? You're supposed

659
00:49:50,287 --> 00:49:51,426
to be preparing the Gusteau recipe.

660
00:49:51,689 --> 00:49:52,859
This is the recipe.

661
00:49:53,123 --> 00:49:54,933
The recipe doesn't call
for white truffle oil!

662
00:49:55,292 --> 00:49:57,511
What else have you...
You are improvising?

663
00:49:57,928 --> 00:50:00,067
This is no time to experiment.
The customer are waiting.

664
00:50:00,464 --> 00:50:02,424
You're right. l should listen to you!

665
00:50:03,634 --> 00:50:04,834
-Stop that!
-Stop what?

666
00:50:05,102 --> 00:50:07,352
Freaking me out!
Whatever you are doing, stop it.

667
00:50:07,771 --> 00:50:09,551
-Where is the special order?
-Coming!

668
00:50:09,907 --> 00:50:11,897
-l thought we were together on this.
-We are together.

669
00:50:12,276 --> 00:50:14,616
-Then what are you doing?
-It's very hard to explain.

670
00:50:15,045 --> 00:50:17,065
-The special?
-Come get it!

671
00:50:19,450 --> 00:50:21,790
Whoa, whoa.
I forgot the anchovy licorice sauce.

672
00:50:27,424 --> 00:50:31,024
-Don't you dare.
-I'm not, I'm not. I'm...

673
00:50:34,632 --> 00:50:35,592
Sorry.

674
00:50:37,668 --> 00:50:39,918
