675
00:50:40,371 --> 00:50:43,001
Ja. It's as bad as we remember.
Just went out.

676
00:50:43,474 --> 00:50:46,634
-Did you taste it?
-Ja, of course, before he changed it.

677
00:50:47,177 --> 00:50:49,637
