678
00:50:50,080 --> 00:50:52,710
He changed it
as it was going out the door!

679
00:50:53,384 --> 00:50:54,234
They love it!

680
00:50:54,451 --> 00:50:56,851
Other diners are already
asking about it, about Linguini.

681
00:50:57,288 --> 00:50:58,838
I have seven more orders!

682
00:50:59,156 --> 00:51:01,466
That's wonderful.

683
00:51:06,430 --> 00:51:07,419
I'd like one of those.

684
00:51:10,167 --> 00:51:11,477
Special order!

685
00:51:15,539 --> 00:51:16,389
What is that?

686
00:51:16,607 --> 00:51:19,507
Special order! Special order!
Special order!

687
00:51:28,252 --> 00:51:29,512
To Linguini.

688
00:51:29,787 --> 00:51:32,037
-Congratulations, Mr. Linguini.
-Cheers, ja?

689
00:51:32,856 --> 00:51:34,586
Drink now, there's plenty.

690
00:51:39,196 --> 00:51:41,276
Take a break, Little Chef. Get some air.

691
00:51:42,633 --> 00:51:44,383
We really did it tonight.

692
00:51:54,578 --> 00:51:55,978
Got your toque.

693
00:51:57,181 --> 00:51:58,381
Oh, seriously now.

694
00:51:58,749 --> 00:52:02,819
