695
00:52:03,487 --> 00:52:05,827
-Am [ in trouble?
-Trouble? No.

696
00:52:06,256 --> 00:52:09,596
A little wine, a friendly chat.
Just us cooks.

697
00:52:11,662 --> 00:52:14,732
The plongeur won't be coming to you
for advice anymore, eh, Colette?

698
00:52:15,265 --> 00:52:17,665
He's gotten all he needs.

699
00:52:20,771 --> 00:52:23,291
Toasting your success, eh, Linguini?

700
00:52:25,142 --> 00:52:26,482
Good for you.

701
00:52:26,777 --> 00:52:30,287
I just took it to be polite.
don't really drink, you know.

702
00:52:30,881 --> 00:52:34,481
Of course you don't.
I wouldn't either if l was drinking that.

703
00:52:35,085 --> 00:52:38,775
But you would have to be an idiot
of elephantine proportions

704
00:52:39,390 --> 00:52:42,930
not to appreciate
this '61 Chateau Latour.

705
00:52:43,627 --> 00:52:47,197
And you, Monsieur Linguini,
are no idiot.

706
00:52:48,632 --> 00:52:51,152
Let us toast your non-idiocy.

707
00:53:15,325 --> 00:53:16,814
-Remy!
-Emile?

708
00:53:17,561 --> 00:53:19,261
I can't believe it! You're alive!

709
00:53:19,596 --> 00:53:20,906
-You made it!
-I thought I'd never see you guys again!

710
00:53:21,198 --> 00:53:22,897
We figured
you didn't survive the rapids.

711
00:53:23,233 --> 00:53:25,133
And what are you eating?

712
00:53:28,272 --> 00:53:29,822
I don't really know.

713
00:53:30,140 --> 00:53:32,950
I think it was
some sort of wrapper once.

714
00:53:33,444 --> 00:53:37,574
What? No.
You're in Paris now, baby. My town.

715
00:53:38,248 --> 00:53:41,318
No brother of mine eats rejectamenta
in my town.

716
00:53:51,261 --> 00:53:54,221
Remy! You are stealing?
You told Linguini he could trust you.

717
00:53:54,732 --> 00:53:58,482
-And he can. It's for my brother.
-But the boy could lose his job.

718
00:53:59,103 --> 00:54:01,883
Which means I would, too.
It's under control, okay?

719
00:54:03,173 --> 00:54:06,653
-More wine?
-l shouldn't, but... Okay.

720
00:54:07,511 --> 00:54:10,441
So, where did you train, Linguini?

721
00:54:10,948 --> 00:54:12,968
Train? All right.

722
00:54:13,484 --> 00:54:17,433
Surely you don't expect me to believe
this is your first time cooking?

723
00:54:18,088 --> 00:54:19,258
-It's not.
-I knew it!

724
00:54:19,523 --> 00:54:22,803
It's my... Second, third, fourth...
Fifth time.

725
00:54:23,360 --> 00:54:24,760
Monday was my first time.

726
00:54:25,062 --> 00:54:27,491
But I've taken out the garbage
lots of times before that...

727
00:54:27,931 --> 00:54:29,921
Yes, yes. Have some more wine.

728
00:54:30,334 --> 00:54:33,144
Tell me, Linguini, about your interests.

729
00:54:33,637 --> 00:54:37,947
-Do you like animals?
-What? Animals? What kind?

730
00:54:39,343 --> 00:54:42,683
The usual, dogs, cats, horses,
. .
guinea pigs,

731
00:54:43,247 --> 00:54:44,267
rats.

